  fhir:description [ fhir:v "Root object of a linear history, i.e. time series structure. This is a generic class whose type parameter must be a descendant of `ITEM_STRUCTURE`, ensuring that each Event in the `_events_` of a given instance is of the same structural type, i.e. `ITEM_TREE`, `ITEM_LIST` etc.\n\nFor a periodic series of events, period will be set, and the time of each Event in the History must correspond; i.e. the `EVENT._offset_` must be a multiple of period for each Event. Missing events in a period History are however allowed. "] ; # 
